                    text="&lt;ul>&lt;li>on page element selection (alternatively in the content tree)&lt;/li>&lt;li>edit content using component related dialogs (like AEM)&lt;/li>&lt;li>add, remove or reorder elements in the tree, the page or in the context view&lt;/li>&lt;li>add component instances or assets via drag and drop from their selections views&lt;/li>&lt;/ul>"
